    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> Finally in our room, we were greeted with a side sea view and a side mountain view. Sometimes nice. We don't have the newest room, but it was very chic - and above all, big. After we unpacked everything, we went in search of something edible. On the way there, we crossed the hotel complex and found that you can't get a single sunbed at lunchtime. Let's see how it will be in the next few days. </p>
        <p> When we arrived at the beach, we completed a short video call with the birthday person at home and then went to the restaurant next to the hotel. Here we shared a really good pizza and a few refreshing drinks. Then we went briefly to the small supermarket around the corner, filled the minibar with water, and then siesta was announced - the inhuman early wake-up time was slowly making itself felt. </p>
        <p> Later we walked along the promenade and looked at what there is to discover for the coming days. Back at the hotel, a really nice buffet was waiting for us - everyone really gets their fill here. And the staff is so friendly that you feel twice as comfortable. </p>
        <p> This is how our vacation starts on the sunny island - relaxed, tasty, and with lots of anticipation for the coming days. </p>
